City Court of Few York, General Term, December, 1899.

Before Fitzsimons, O. J., and Hasoall, J.

Ferdinand Elsterman, Respondent, v. Cornelius Kahlen, Appellant.

Appeal from a I judgment in favor of plaintiff. Charles I Oakes, for Appellant; Heyn & Covington I (Herbert A. Heyn of counsel), for Respond ent Judgment affirmed, with costs. No opinion.
